searchData={"items":[{"type":"module","title":"Chpter","doc":"","ref":"Chpter.html"},{"type":"function","title":"Chpter.check_for_payment/2","doc":"","ref":"Chpter.html#check_for_payment/2"},{"type":"function","title":"Chpter.initiate_payment/8","doc":"","ref":"Chpter.html#initiate_payment/8"},{"type":"extras","title":"Chpter","doc":"# Chpter\n\nPhoenix(Elixir) wrapper for chpter API implimentatio for Mpesa Payments in Kenya.","ref":"readme.html"},{"type":"extras","title":"Installation - Chpter","doc":"The package can be installed\nby adding `chpter` to your list of dependencies in `mix.exs`:\n\n```elixir\ndef deps do\n  [\n    {:chpter, \"~> 0.1.0\"}\n  ]\nend\n```\n\nRun `mix deps.get` to fetch from Hex","ref":"readme.html#installation"},{"type":"extras","title":"Usage - Chpter","doc":"This is broken down into two parts:\n\n#","ref":"readme.html#usage"},{"type":"extras","title":"1. Initiation - Chpter","doc":"There is a function called `initiate_payment` that takes in the following parameters:\n\n- `api_key` - Your Chpter API key\n- `phone_number` - The phone number to send the payment request to\n- `name` - The name of the person to send the payment request to\n- `email` - The email of the person to send the payment request to\n- `amount` - The amount to be paid\n- `callback_url` - The callback url to be used by Chpter to send the payment request response to\n- `transaction_reference` - The reference to be used for the payment request\n\n```elixir\n iex> Chpter.initiate_payment(\n         \"pk_4aff02227456f6b499820c2621ae181c9e35666d25865575fef47622265dcbb9\",\n          \"254740769596\",\n         \"Michael Munavu\",\n         \"michaelmunavu83@gmail.com\",\n           1,\n        \"https://720a-102-135-173-116.ngrok-free.app/api/transactions\",\n         \"123456\")\n\n```\n\n#","ref":"readme.html#1-initiation"},{"type":"extras","title":"2. Checking Transaction Status - Chpter","doc":"There is a function called `check_for_payment` that takes in the following parameters:\n\n- `api_endpoint` - The Chpter API endpoint where all the transactions are stored\n- `transaction_reference` - The reference to be used for the payment request\n\n```elixir\n iex> Chpter.check_for_payment(\n         \"https://api.chpter.co/v1/transactions\",\n         \"123456\")\n\n```","ref":"readme.html#2-checking-transaction-status"},{"type":"extras","title":"Documentation - Chpter","doc":"[https://hexdocs.pm/mpesa](https://hexdocs.pm/mpesa/Mpesa.html).","ref":"readme.html#documentation"},{"type":"extras","title":"AUthor - Chpter","doc":"[Michael Munavu](https://michaelmunavu.com)","ref":"readme.html#author"},{"type":"extras","title":"Licence - Chpter","doc":"Chpter is released under [MIT License](https://github.com/appcues/exsentry/blob/master/LICENSE.txt)","ref":"readme.html#licence"}],"content_type":"text/markdown"}